data.description:
Looking for a comfortable place to call home? Look no further than this 3 bedroom 2 bath house, situated on a quiet cul-de-sac. New Roof 2019, HVAC Replaced 2017 with 16 SEER unit and heat pump, NEST smart thermostat and hot water heater in 2020. The backyard retaining wall replacement was completed in July 2021, the dishwasher in 2020, and the refrigerator in 2016. 
Inside you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area with a wall of windows, perfect for spending time with family or entertaining guests. The eat-in kitchen features plenty of counter space for all your cooking needs. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer ample closet space.
Outside, you'll find a fenced-in backyard with room for outdoor activities and relaxation. The cul-de-sac location means minimal traffic and a peaceful atmosphere for you to enjoy. This home truly has it all, with its convenient location and move-in-ready status. Don't miss your opportunity to make this house your new home.
